			<div class="commentcount">16</div>

				<p>Next time, you might want to consider just making a milkshake, also known as my Mom&#8217;s Fancy Milk Punch. The best vanilla ice cream you can find, bourbon, nutmeg, whole milke (or hlaf n half or light cream also work well): whiz it up in a blender and voila! Milk Punch. No extra freezing time required!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
